notes/Nginx/proxy/Upstream-Keepalive.content:
To enable keepalive connections to upstream, the keepalive directive must be included in upstream{} blocks, and in the location{} blocks you need to switch HTTP version to 1.1 and clear the default Connection: close request header set by Nginx. See Headers.
proxy_http_version 1.1;
proxy_set_header   &quot;Connection&quot; &quot;&quot;;

